combine

public static List<ICacheKeyGenerator> combine(List<ICacheKeyGenerator> a,
                                               List<ICacheKeyGenerator> b)
Returns a new list containing the results of combining each element in a with the corresponding element in b. If the result contains the same elements as a, then a is returned.

The input arrays must be the same length, and the types of the array elements at each index must be the same

b -
Returns:
The list of combined cache key generators
